	dprr:hasNoteText "An aged senator in 76 (MRR 2.493). Sumner points out that in Cic. Rosc. Com. 43-49, the mss readings vary between Manlius and Manilius and may refer to an elder T. Manlius Torquatus (Orators 130-131).\n" .
